    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s been truly loved? I\u2019m parting with this absolute gem and it's in wonderful shape! It\u2019s been super well-maintained, runs like a dream, and is ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. It\u2019s clean, comfy, and honestly just a joy to drive. I'd love for it to go to a great home, so feel free to reach out if you want to come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
