      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and a high-revving valvetrain. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain remains robust with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes reinforced rear subframe mounting points and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul to ensure optimal cam timing. The suspension retains its factory-tuned poise with refreshed bushings, while the cross-drilled rotors provide consistent thermal management under load. A driver-focused example that balances mechanical purity with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Reliable runner.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of its model year. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper consistent with careful highway use. Inside, the cabin remains a smoke-free environment; the premium leather upholstery is intact and supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. Every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has a full service history, with a recent oil change and a comprehensive multi-point inspection just completed. The tires offer plenty of tread life, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. This is a solid, honest car ready for its next owner to drive away with peace of mind.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
